{"tid":169032,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係配有民主咩?","createTime":"2017-03-24T02:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T09:18:48.000Z","uid":28264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa97fcb39ebeb57406c675b5c1de7bf895610ad5","tid":169032,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T02:53:46.000Z","msg":"利申左先 唔係支持 羅冠聰 但真係幾過引<br />\n<br />\n特首選舉雖然同大家都沒關 不過班友既言論真係好好笑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493.1073741828.627043070780363/991982044286462/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fphotos%2Fa.645858435565493.1073741828.627043070780363%2F991982044286462%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c0c53564\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493.1073741828.627043070780363/991982044286462/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVV50pU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVV50pU.png&h=cc6791ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎選啦 香港人都仲未明特首選舉係點玩 仲以為係票高就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁簡單既一個制度 有等於或多於601票就贏 <br />\n得1200票 姐係只會有1個人可以達到601票 沒人達到601就重選<br />\n咁簡單既規距都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只要林病有601票 餘下果599 你點投 投比邊個根本就沒分別 咁都唔明 <br />\n咁點比民主你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連咁簡單既特首選舉制度都唔明 <br />\n唔好話咩 全面民下更復雜既選舉制度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7aa5676589f215b5b10ba10f787e5c7d11578b7","tid":169032,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T02:59:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a84015042b42224041acbde58ced07e34c65322","tid":169032,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply